Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.24,0:00:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢你陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是一个人去买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉看看就满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.12,0:00:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.29,0:00:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个人的时候也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.75,0:00:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找个地方喝下午茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.63,0:00:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.92,0:00:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近有什么店来着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新开的汉堡店
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.06,0:00:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.14,0:00:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里的奶昔好像超级好暍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.94,0:00:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听说了吗 犬塚老师的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.24,0:00:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说去年他妻子去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.78,0:00:43.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.91,0:00:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.00,0:00:53.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.21,0:00:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.48,0:01:07.91,Top,,0,0,0,,开往高尾的中央特快即将到达12号线 请注意安全 退到黄线之后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.51,0:01:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经一年了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,爱意满满的御好烧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.41,0:03:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师和小紬希吃过饭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉 已经这个时候了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.47,0:03:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肚子饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.52,0:03:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.98,0:03:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.19,0:03:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸今天有点累了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.49,0:03:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去外面吃好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.99,0:03:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没在外面吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都是爸爸在做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在小鸟家也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家庭餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:54.04,Top,,0,0,0,,拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:56.00,Top,,0,0,0,,意面工坊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想 去哪里好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里味道好香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御好烧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御好烧是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对哦 我们家没做过这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用喜欢的东西烧什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 用喜欢的配料和美味的面粉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,配料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.07,0:04:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉啊 墨鱼啊 虾什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己动手把它们搅拌搅拌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放到烫烫的铁板上滋滋地烧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:30.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希觉得自己能做这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.13,0:04:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们进去试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请坐这边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:45.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里滋滋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希小姐 很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么还不来啊 对吧 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:04:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.53,0:05:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的猪肉墨鱼鸡蛋御好烧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搅拌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家店是做好了送上来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搅拌搅拌和白己滋滋烧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 店员已经帮我们做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被爸爸骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 说的真不好听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是事先不知道而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 我明明可以自己动手的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.94,0:05:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 你能撒青海苔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 撒太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧 我要自己来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希 不能乱玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你看 搞砸了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:06:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等等等 别哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸的跟你换 你快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 紬希
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:16.21,Top,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 吃这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:22.93,Top,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 紬希 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.79,0:06:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没怎么吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬塚先生 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.72,0:06:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 小紬希
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 没什么精神呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.99,0:07:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 其实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈下周好像能空出时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说也想来参加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 你说做饭会是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 就是有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咋天和紬希吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵架 这次又是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一不小心大声说了她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她弄哭以后 我也惊慌失措
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么做饭会 我们就做御好烧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御好烧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次吃御好烧就留下那样的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:07:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就太让人难过了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实 你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来挽回名誉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道她愿不愿意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希 今天幼儿园怎么样呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小优花她说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小优花的妈妈从来不训她 很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干雄君的妈妈像恶魔 会训人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然爸爸不会无缘无故地发怒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但紬希做错事的时候 我会训人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我真的好想做滋滋烧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 所以下次做饭会我们准备做御好烧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 饭田女士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说小鸟同学的妈妈和小鹿忍同学也会来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鸟妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸也是第一次见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬紬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小忍 我好想你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我妈妈稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是因为工作出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小八木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说她今天在才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我透的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了算了 别这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小八木 我们一起做饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 你们只做御好烧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 食材在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做猪肉墨鱼鸡蛋御好烧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小鸟你们就做这个猪肉墨鱼鸡蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们随便做点不同的搭配出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.76,0:10:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是指…我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 动手动手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 取高汤冷却
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高汤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是事先冷却好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,低筋面粉过筛 装进碗里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意不要结疙瘩 一点点加入高场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 注意不要结疙瘩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前你帮我施过不结疙瘩的咒语吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:58.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想看想看 怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.09,0:11:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样 这 这样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.01,0:11:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疙瘩 疙瘩 不要变成疙瘩哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要变 疙瘩疙瘩疙瘩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疙瘩疙瘩之舞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你施咒语
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要 反正我不会弄出疙瘩来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希 那个 你继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.99,0:11:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去看一看小八木
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:37.19,Top,,0,0,0,,我说了不用 去找你爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 疙瘩 疙瘩 不要变成疙瘩哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 我想看小八木和小忍这边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这边就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山 山药擦成泥 拌匀之后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把面团稍微放一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卷心菜就拜托老师了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:11:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 切菜的速度变快了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 切菜熟练起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.49,0:12:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小八木切得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险 你脸靠太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 继续切 继续切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真 真寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 毕竟行家的刀工看着就很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反而 是你没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.09,0:12:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈妈说她来不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也还没好好跟她打过招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就知道她很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.23,0:12:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她今天告诉我来不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明可以再提前一点告诉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉自己不被她重视
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.41,0:13:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这么说出来 总感觉特别小孩子气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 戳中了我的痛点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:11.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得 你妈妈一定不是不重视你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能只是手忙脚乱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直很珍视对方的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传达也好 化为行动也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都很困难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希也会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要做嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这就是俗话说的「儿女不知父母心」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这样也好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道或许比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果太懂得父母心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.05,0:13:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害她烦恼就太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:13:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这句话不是在夸我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在夸你在夸你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.07,0:14:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:15.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太碍事了 一边去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬紬的脚碰到了碗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.33,0:14:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事洗洗就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「对不起」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希 你讨厌被训吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,0:15:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸也讨厌训人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.16,0:15:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.58,0:15:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 刚刚是紬希做了坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸说过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希要是做错事 我是会训人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然紬希过厌被训 爸爸也讨厌训人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你做错事的话 我会努力训你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来爸爸也讨厌训人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 之前在御好烧店里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候 爸爸没能很好地训你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.16,0:15:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸训得不好 这一点很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.96,0:15:58.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希也对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有小八木 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.81,0:16:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去给你爸帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.36,0:16:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搅拌 搅拌 搅拌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.95,0:16:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成一体 搅拌拌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸也唱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搅拌 搅拌 搅拌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鸟也一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搅拌 搅拌 搅拌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成一体 搅拌拌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搅拌 搅拌 搅拌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.93,0:16:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成一体 搅拌拌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.06,0:16:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滋滋的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.48,0:17:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放上五花肉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.49,0:17:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滋滋滋滋 烧啊烧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翻面之后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盖上盖子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后再翻一次面 烧过之后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.21,0:17:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涂上满满的酱汁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挤上蛋黄酱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后用这个「眦」地一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.56,0:17:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬希也要做这个 想做这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 小紬希
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.98,0:17:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.86,0:17:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在烧下一个 你们可以先吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.08,0:17:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧趁热吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.75,0:18:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶 赶上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎各位光临
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.68,0:18:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是犬塚老师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是受您家照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里 我才是女儿一直受您照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里哪里 我女儿才一直受照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.82,0:18:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 抱歉打招呼晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:31.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫犬塚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.49,0:18:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您言重了 我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.87,0:18:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是饭田小鸟的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饭田惠 真人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.04,0:18:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.42,0:18:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是小紬希吧 初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.38,0:18:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鸟妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 我是犬塚紬希
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你和小鸟做好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.89,0:19:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作结束的比较早
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今早那么突然真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.28,0:19:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以参加吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.87,0:19:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去准备宴厅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 那身衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为慌慌张张赶时间 穿着拍摄服装就回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去换一身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.18,0:19:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.22,0:19:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从哪个开始吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.73,0:19:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是小八木做的 加了牛腱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是小鸟妈妈放了蘑菇哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从紬希帮了忙的猪肉墨鱼鸡蛋御好烧开始吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猪肉墨鱼鸡蛋耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.72,0:20:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.43,0:20:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比店里的更好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 是不是过奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.77,0:20:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.44,0:20:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小紬希的爸爸做的御好烧这么好吃 是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里面包含了对小紬希满满的爱意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.08,0:20:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是小鸟妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面不改色地就说出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.30,0:20:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.26,0:20:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.72,0:21:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱意就是爱吗
